---
title: Asian Sweet-Soy Pork & Broccoli Stir-Fry with Jasmine Rice & Crispy Shallots
description: We love a tender bit of broccoli in our pork stir-fry and we hope you’ll agree that it lends the perfect veggie touch to this one. We can’t forget the crunch of the crispy shallots, because all these elements together help to make a stir-fry
we simply adore.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
